  # - `A1`: 23.4in x 33.1in
  # - `A2`: 16.54in x 23.4in
  # - `A3`: 11.7in x 16.54in
  # - `A4`: 8.27in x 11.7in
  # - `A5`: 5.83in x 8.27in
